divs: Sighting Detailson the 3rd sept 10 at 21.17 i was in my garden and i noticed a bright light in the sky I took picture 1 as it came towards me and picture 2 when it was overhead.it was a quiet night and i did not hear any noise from the object nor did i see any landing lights. I would appreciate it if you could have a look and let me know what you think it could be.
trends: There have been no other sightings in Maidstone
